{"tid":180263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港地連90後都買到樓，你買唔到因為你廢！","createTime":"2017-03-30T23:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T12:56:26.000Z","uid":29314,"like":6,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc033a7217c7e066f6da808fcad7fcada4432883","tid":180263,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T23:03:20.000Z","msg":"係香港只要你肯做，<br />\n正正常常大學生Fresh Grad月薪3萬以上，<br />\n做多幾年加薪到4/5萬一個月。<br />\n<br />\n只要你肯光合作用，減少消費，<br />\n儲幾個月都有40萬夠俾首期，<br />\n30歲前買樓不是夢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔自住放租，<br />\n再儲首期無限loop，<br />\n一開二、二開四、四四一十六&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解人地90後大學生Fresh Grad就有錢買樓而你唔得？<br />\n<br />\n每年買新手機、<br />\n每年去幾次旅行、<br />\n每星期入戲院睇戲、<br />\n個個週末食放題、<br />\n日鳩日去shopping&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n緊係儲唔到首期啦。<br />\n<br />\n香港起冇天災、冇戰爭、冇恐襲，<br />\n就算香港樓價係5萬蚊呎我都覺得值得係超值！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好再怨香港樓價點解咁貴，<br />\n你地應該怨自己點解咁廢買唔到樓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同請分享。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5389af14804ead0ed3997bb8fa63b3de7ee108e","tid":180263,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T23:09:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3eede3ac5f94ec2f451b011d23fe15f2b7e28817","tid":180263,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T23:10:55.000Z","msg":"Fresh grad咩工有三萬up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2a505e3749c89fcd23a6fe86a09f7eb4688e84","tid":180263,"uid":74172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T23:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fresh grad咩工有三萬up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有醫護人員"},{"pid":"8634e71425f7a97bbffd71c85f1bb51d85feea91","tid":180263,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T23:43:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8476171f7d58d303805e7dbd33084295521576fa","tid":180263,"uid":5650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco